data.description: Discover a stylish 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath craftsman home in Forsyth County, Georgia. Built in 2018, this modern and classy residence is nestled between the lively Gainesville, rich in new restaurants and entertainment, and the serene Dawsonville. Each bedroom features its own full bathroom, and the fenced backyard adds an extra layer of privacy. The kitchen is a dream with white shaker cabinets, granite countertops, and a deep sink. Energy efficiency is key in this home, reducing utility costs. It’s close to Lake Lanier boat ramps, making it ideal for water enthusiasts. Located in an area with sought-after schools and the new East Forsyth High School.
